    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UFOs are attacking the City, Go get 'em!  Single Player OR Multiplayer Jet Fighter Game with A.I. UFO Bots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP or COOP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly different types of Jets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Guns and Missiles to defeat them to win !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb Your way to the top, shoot and hunt enemies in a multiplayer match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be challenged to determine the best pilot who destroys the other jet fighters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take Your Jet to new heights, the sky is NO Limit !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* This game is part of the &quot;Jets&quot; mini-series event from Archor Games, be sure to check it out on Steam! *</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*** UPDATE #9 : Updated Internet Multiplayer via Latest Steam Online Subsystem &amp; Upgraded to Unreal 5.x ***  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make Sure You Have the Latest Version of Steam Installed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need a Solid &amp; Fast Internet Connection for best results.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*************************************************************************</p>",
